Class FbUrlType

java.lang.Object
  ezvcard.types.VCardType
      ezvcard.types.TextType
          ezvcard.types.UriType
              ezvcard.types.FbUrlType
All Implemented Interfaces:
HasAltId, Comparable<VCardType>
public class FbUrlType
extends UriType
implements HasAltId

A URL that shows when the person is free/busy on their calendar.

Code sample 

 VCard vcard = new VCard();
 FbUrlType fburl = new FbUrlType("http://www.example.com/freebusy/janedoe");
 vcard.addFbUrl(fburl);

Property name: FBURL

Supported versions: 4.0

Author:
Michael Angstadt
